import React from 'react';
import { Parallax } from 'react-parallax';
import LeftPanelBg from '../../images/LeftPanel.png';
import ParaBgIcon from '../../images/ParaBackground.png';
import VerticalName from '../../images/NameVertical.png';
import BackgroundPic from '../../images/BackgroundPara.jpg';
import {
  AboutContainer,
  AboutWrapper,
  AboutContRight,
  AboutContMiddle,
  AboutContLeft,
  AboutContTop,
  AboutContBottom,
  AboutCardTop,
  AboutCardBottom,
  AboutCardInTop,
  AboutCardInBottom,
  AboutH1,
  AboutH2Top,
  AboutH2Bottom,
  AboutIcon,
  AboutIcon2
} from './AboutElements';

const About = () => {
  return (
    <Parallax bgImage={BackgroundPic} strength={500}>
    <AboutContainer id='about'>
      <AboutWrapper>
        <AboutContLeft>
          <AboutIcon src={LeftPanelBg}/>
        </AboutContLeft>
        <AboutContMiddle>
          <AboutContTop>
            <AboutH1>My Story</AboutH1>
          </AboutContTop>
          <AboutContBottom>
            <AboutCardTop>
              <AboutCardInTop>
                <AboutH2Top>
                  The future1community vision was realized in 2016 when Mr. Gospel Gordah realized an unusual statistic 
                  regarding Minnesota. Our state has zero minorty atheletic clubs. In other states you will always find one or two
                  minorty operated sports clubs.
                </AboutH2Top>
              </AboutCardInTop>
            </AboutCardTop>
            <AboutCardBottom>
              <AboutCardInBottom>
                <AboutH2Bottom>
                  Our hopes is to make Minnesota leader in having the most minorty sports club. We hope to accomplish this feat through
                  obtaining large federal grants for minorty charter schools, and taking a hands on approach with builiding athletics 
                  departments for these charter schools. We plan to mentor and train these schools faculties.
                </AboutH2Bottom>
              </AboutCardInBottom>
            </AboutCardBottom>
          </AboutContBottom>
        </AboutContMiddle> 
        <AboutContRight>
          <Parallax bgImage={VerticalName} strength={-500}>
          <AboutIcon2 src ={ParaBgIcon}/>
          </Parallax>
        </AboutContRight>
      </AboutWrapper>     
    </AboutContainer>
    </Parallax>
    
  );
};

export default About;
